---
name: QR Power Cards — Dynamic Sheet Integration
description: QR scanner fetches card definitions from 'קלפים' Google Sheet (GID 984041122) and matches scanned barcodes dynamically
type: feature
---
- Cards are fetched from the 'קלפים' sheet via fetchCardData() in fetchGameData.ts
- GameCard type: { action, url, description, cardKey }
- Scanned codes are matched against sheet data first, then fall back to hardcoded aliases
- handleCardEffect() executes game state changes and returns satirical breaking news headlines
- PowerActivatedOverlay accepts dynamic cardType (string) + optional cardLabel
- Sheet GIDs: trivia=962320107, cards=984041122, missions=600327577, debates=410013963
- Placeholder fetchMissionData() ready for future 'משימות' sheet implementation
- Both QrScannerModal and ScanCard page support unknown card keys from the sheet
